Deborah DAILEY, Petitioner
v.
CITY OF PHILADELPHIA BOARD OF PENSIONS AND RETIREMENT, Respondent No. 581 EAL 2018 Supreme Court of Pennsylvania. May 22, 2019

ORDER

PER CURIAM .

AND NOW, this 22nd day of May, 2019, the Petition for Allowance of Appeal is DENIED.
